52bac363-d024-4f4e-a5b0-b6f31a2d79d5.text:
Oh! Please hire me! I'm very good, well, I'm
not bad, and my fee's only 1000 coins.

options.text: Tell me about your previous jobs

4f02753d-424d-4ce4-bb9a-fb9872320fc1.title: Maid
4f02753d-424d-4ce4-bb9a-fb9872320fc1.text:
Oh! Oh dear! I'm terribly sorry, but I'm not
allowed to work for anyone unless they have level 25
Construction. If a house is poorly made I might damage
it by mistake!

7f322838-510b-4f87-8cc0-5a2c77b60dc1.title: Maid
7f322838-510b-4f87-8cc0-5a2c77b60dc1.text: Alright. I can start work immediately.

args: &cYou must have a home to do that.
&cYou need a second bedroom with a bed for your servant to sleep in.
&cYou do not have enough coins to do that.

9f6c476d-8fa8-4bd3-b49b-e548da18f8b9.text:
Oh! Oh! I, well, I, er. It wasn't really my fault, I mean,
it was, but not really. I mean, how was I to know that
that plate was so valuable? It was just lying around and
I don't know art, it just looked like a pretty pattern and

96884028-72c7-4e1e-9a1d-76f1fd4c54db.title: Maid
96884028-72c7-4e1e-9a1d-76f1fd4c54db.text:
Well, I can, um. I can cook meals and make tea and
everything, and I can even take things to and from the
bank for you. I won't make any mistakes this time and
everything will be fine!

94e08a2f-9150-480b-a42c-70d54f4ce9a5.title: Maid
94e08a2f-9150-480b-a42c-70d54f4ce9a5.text:
I just had to use it because there weren't enough
plates. And no one had told me that Dennis was off sick
and hadn't fed the dogs so I wasn't expecting them to
jump up at me when I was carrying the food and it, it

2d13ec5e-95fb-4151-8b56-f10d8b68848e.title: Maid
2d13ec5e-95fb-4151-8b56-f10d8b68848e.text:
went all over the place, gravy and potatoes and bits of
